data.text:
At Erik’s, we want to make sure that the little ones enjoy a fresh and delicious meal along with the grown-ups. Our Kid’s Meals are for children 12 and under and gives three tasty options which include a choice of milk or water.

Because our suppliers are not required to disclose the origin of all contents in their products we are unable to safely state the contents of every product.
